description: Lists an environment's completed and failed managed actions.

nested_items.name: ManagedActionHistoryItems
nested_items.description: A list of completed and failed managed actions.

nested_items.name: ActionId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the managed action.

nested_items.name: ActionType
nested_items.description: The type of the managed action.

nested_items.name: ActionDescription
nested_items.description: A description of the managed action.

nested_items.name: FailureType
nested_items.description: If the action failed, the type of failure.

nested_items.name: FailureDescription
nested_items.description: If the action failed, a description of the failure.

nested_items.name: ExecutedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the action started executing.

nested_items.name: FinishedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the action finished executing.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token that you pass to  DescribeEnvironmentManagedActionHistory to get the next page of results.
